Package: SimulatoR
Type: Package
Title: Generate Simulated Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Michael Kammer [aut, cre]
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Kammer", 
    email = "michael.kammer@meduniwien.ac.at", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Michael Kammer <michael.kammer@meduniwien.ac.at>
Description: Generate simulated datasets from a multivariate gaussian
    distribution using a simple way to specify their correlation structure
    and apply transformations to obtain realistic data. Simple network
    visualization tools are provided to facilitate communicating the setup.
